com.exlibris.dps.sdk.techmd

Interface TechnicalMDExtractorPlugin

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MDExtractorPlugin

    public interface TechnicalMDExtractorPlugin

    Interface for metadata extractors. Each extractor handles a specific format and extracts its attributes.
    This plugin interface only supports java implementation.

      • extract

        void extract(java.lang.String file)
      throws java.lang.Exception
        Extracts a file's attributes according to the given file path. Extraction of all attributes relevant to the format implementation.
        The attribute values can be given using the getAttributeByName(String) method
        Parameters:
        file - the file path to extract
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - if an unexpected exception occurs, such as IOException.
